          "datePublished": "2023-04-04",
          "reviewRating": {
            "@type": "Rating",
            "ratingValue": "5",
            "bestRating": "5",
            "worstRating": "1"
          },
          "reviewBody": "So I am a student at TSMS and I FREAKING LOVE IT. the teachers handle us in a certain way that we don't hate them but we stay quiet.  We can talk to our friends and our exam system us good too. They make a lot of effort for us to enjoy even if it is cringey",
          "publisher": {
            "@type": "Organization",
            "name": "Yellow Slate"
          }
        },
        {
          "@type": "Review",
          "itemReviewed": {
            "@type": "School",
            "name": "The Shriram Millennium School - Section 135"
          },
          "author": {
            "@type": "Person",
            "name": "pallavi chauhan"
          },
          "datePublished": "2022-09-15",
          "reviewRating": {
            "@type": "Rating",
            "ratingValue": "1",
            "bestRating": "5",
            "worstRating": "1"
          },
          "reviewBody": "To begin with must inform to all parents that it's not original Shriram school, it's a partnership of Shri educare and millenium group. That's why you will find different websites for TSRS and TSMS. Nonetheless, I had applied for admission for my child and found that the school staff is quite smug and take too much pride in themselves, they would just evaluate the child however do not want to take time out to sit with parents, brief on their pedagogy and approach towards teaching etc. School tour is worthless with an office boy taking you around the school, the facilities and infra are anyway below par compared to other new age schools in Noida. It is totally cramped and most classrooms do not even have proper sunlight. If you start asking questions from teachers on teaching style etc. they start getting irritated and would just want to get over with it. They are just minting money on the brand name no real value addition in terms of holistic growth of child.",
          "publisher": {
            "@type": "Organization",
            "name": "Yellow Slate"
          }
        },
        {
          "@type": "Review",
          "itemReviewed": {
            "@type": "School",
            "name": "The Shriram Millennium School - Section 135"
          },
          "author": {
            "@type": "Person",
            "name": "kanchan sonwani"
          },
          "datePublished": "2022-04-11",
          "reviewRating": {
            "@type": "Rating",
            "ratingValue": "5",
            "bestRating": "5",
            "worstRating": "1"
          },
          "reviewBody": "The environment of TSMS is very warm and welcoming allowing students to grow in a safe and secure environment. My daughter has benefited immensely from the research based and structured learning environment provided by the school that makes her think on her own. I would definitely recommend this best IGCSE school in Noida.",
          "publisher": {
            "@type": "Organization",
            "name": "Yellow Slate"
          }
        },
        {
          "@type": "Review",
          "itemReviewed": {
            "@type": "School",
