            "bestRating": "5",
            "worstRating": "1"
          },
          "reviewBody": "The infrastructure of the school is well maintained. The school is resourced with modern facilities with well equipped labs, sports fields and play areas, libraries, computer centers, music and dance rooms and so on. Therefore, our overall experience with TSMS has been spectacular. Definitely recommended!",
